---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section id="work">
    <h1>Clients</h1>
		<div class="container">
      {[
        {
          href: "https://jauntin.com/",
          imgSrc: "/projects/Jauntin.png",
          title: "Jauntin",
          className: 'project-card--jauntin',
          copy: <div>
            <p>Jauntin unlocks new revenue channels for insurers. They help identify which insurance products are suitable for digitization and embedding into third party platforms.</p>
            <p>
              We introduced AI to enhance insurer operations, including anomaly detection and intelligent search. We also architected UI standards and dynamic forms designed to manage complex, multi-entity data with rich business parameters — delivering a seamless experience for both insurance purchasers and administrative staff.
            </p>
          </div>
        },
        {
          href: "https://avesdo.com/",
          imgSrc: "/projects/Avesdo.png",
          title: "Avesdo",
          copy: <p>Avesdo is a SaaS platform tailored for new home sales. They help developers and sales agencies manage the entire sales process—from lead capture to contract management.</p>
                <p>
                  We led and collaborated on multiple UI initiatives across several SaaS products. We modernized legacy systems and built scalable architecture to manage complex and data-heavy workflows.
                </p>
        },
        {
          href: "https://www.realosophy.com/",
          imgSrc: "/projects/Realosophy.svg",
          title: "Realosophy",
          copy: 
          <p>Realosophy is an independent, full-service real estate brokerage company. Their website provides valuable data-driven insights and analysis helping consumers make better real estate decisions.</p>
          <p>
            We built software solutions that transformed complex real estate data into interactive, map-driven research tools. We also developed internal systems and third-party integrations to streamline operations and support sales growth.
          </p>        },
    ].map(({ imgSrc, copy, href, title, className }) =>
        <div class={`project-card ${className && className}`}>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="project-card__logo-wrapper">
              <a href={href} class="project-card__logo" title={title} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                <img src={imgSrc} />
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card__copy col-12 col-md-8 flex-center py-4">
              {copy}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      )}
		</div>
  </section>
</Layout>
<style lang="scss">
  .project-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    margin-top: 2rem;

    &:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }

    .row {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    &__logo-wrapper {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    &__logo {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;

      img {
        max-width: 140px;
        height: auto;
        object-fit: contain;
      }
    }

    &__copy {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--color-text);
    }

    // Desktop
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .row {
        flex-direction: row;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: left;
      }

      &__logo-wrapper {
        flex: 0 0 220px;
        margin-bottom: 0;
        margin-right: 2rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      &__logo {
        img {
          max-width: 180px;
        }
      }

      &__copy {
        flex: 1;
      }
    }
  }
</style>

